# Chrome Extension Guardrails

- Do not rewrite proven mode/config logic unless the harness proves a regression.
- Do not add tactical upload fallbacks without tests.
- Keep runtime handshake, selector registry, telemetry lockdown, and upload strategy aligned with the active phase docs.
- No live UAT as a substitute for local proof.
